data.description: Under Construction Don't miss you chance to own this beautiful 3 bedroom,2 bath Lennar new construction home. This spacious and lovely home is filled with upgrades including double-pane windows, GreenGaurd Max house wrap, hybrid water heater, Mohawk green certified, plush, wall-to-wall carpeting, designer light fixtures, and a GE washer and dryer included! Enjoy hosting friends and family in your open concept living area, with your stylish kitchen featuring GE Stainless Steel appliances, 42" maple panel wood cabinets, stainless steel under-mount kitchen sink, granite counter tops and full decorative back splash.  Your master suite will be your own personal hideaway. Your master bathroom features maple wood cabinets, designer brushed-nickel plumbing fixtures, granite counter tops, designer light fixtures, oval under-mount sink bowls, and a semi-frameless, clear glass shower enclosure! Spend time enjoying all your community has to offer such lazy river, water-slides, swim-up bar, water falls, beach entry, spa, splash pad, grill, bar, fitness area, theater, game rooms, Tiki bar and cabanas. All amenities are included in the HOA! All located close to major attractions in gorgeous Champions Gate, Florida! Make your appointment today!
